Two young men were on Saturday caught by some residents of Abeokuta for alleged robbery. They were said to have been arrested by the people around Ibara GRA after they had attacked no fewer than two landlords in the area. According to a video made available to DAILY POST correspondent, the men were three in number, operating with a motorcycle to aid their escape after robbing victims. It was gathered that one of them was able to escape with the motorbike, while the two others arrested were seriously beaten before they were taken to the police station. See video: